 Centre]], [[Halifax Regional Municipality|Halifax]]\n\n====Ontario====\n* [[Canadian Museum of Nature]], [[Ottawa]]\n* [[Canada Science and Technology Museum]], Ottawa\n* [[Ontario Science Centre]], [[Toronto]]\n* [[Personal Computer Museum]], [[Brantford, Ontario|Brantford]]\n* [[Science North]] and [[Dynamic Earth]] in [[Greater Sudbury|Sudbury]]\n* [[Canada South Science City]] in [[Windsor, Ontario|Windsor]]\n\n====Saskatchewan====\n* [[Saskatchewan Science Centre]], [[Regina, Saskatchewan|Regina]]\n\n====Quebec====\n* [[Cosmodome (Laval)]], [[Quebec]]\n* [[Mont M\u00e9gantic Observatory]], [[Notre-Dame-des-Bois, Quebec|Notre-Dame-des-Bois]]\n\n===United States===\n{{Main article|List of science museums in the United States}}\n\n==Asia and Oceania==\n\n===Australia===\n* [[Macleay Museum]]&nbsp;\u2013 Sydney University Museums, [[Sydney]]\n* [[Melbourne Museum]], [[Melbourne]]\n* [[Powerhouse Museum]], [[Sydney]]\n* [[Queensland Museum]], [[Brisbane]]\n* [[Questacon]]&nbsp;\u2013 The National Science and Technology Centre, [[Canberra]]\n* [[Scienceworks Museum (Melbourne)|Scienceworks Museum]], [[Melbourne]]\n* [[Scitech]], [[Perth, Western Australia|Perth]]\n* [[South Australian Museum]], [[Adelaide]]\n* [[Science Space]], [[Wollongong, NSW]]\n\n===China===\n* [[China Science and Technology Museum]], [[Beijing]]\n* [[Beijing Museum of Natural History]]\n* [[Shanghai Science and Technology Museum]], [[Pudong]], Shanghai\n* [[Sichuan Science and Technology Museum]], [[Sichuan]]\n* [[Guangdong Science Center]], [[Guangzhou]]\n\n===Hong Kong===\n* [[Health Education Exhibition and Resource Centre]], [[Kowloon Park]]\n* [[Hong Kong Museum of Medical Sciences]], [[Mid-levels]]\n* [[Fanling Environmental Resource Centre]], [[Fanling]]\n* [[Hong Kong Science Museum]], [[Tsim Sha Tsui]]\n* [[Hong Kong Space Museum]], [[Tsim Sha Tsui]]\n\n===India===\n* [[Birla Industrial & Technological Museum]], [[Kolkata]]\n* [[Birla Science Museum]], [[Hyderabad, India|Hyderabad]]\n