o]]\n* [[Gwacheon National Science Museum]], [[Gyeonggi-do]]\n* [[Gwangju National Museum]], [[Gwangju]]\n* [[Incheon Children's Science Museum]], [[Incheon]]\n* [[National Busan Science Museum]], [[Busan]]\n* [[National Daegu Science Museum]], [[Daegu]]\n* [[Sachuan Advanced Aerospace Science Museum]], [[Gyeongsangnam-do]]\n* [[Seoul Science Museum]], [[Seoul]]\n* [[Ulsan Science Museum]], [[Ulsan]]\n* [[Uljin Science Experience Center]], [[Gyeongsangbuk-do]]\n\n===Taiwan===\n* [[Insect Science Museum]], [[Taipei]]\n* [[National Museum of Marine Science and Technology]], [[Keelung]]\n* [[National Taiwan Science Education Center]], [[Taipei]]\n* [[National Museum of Natural Science]], [[Taichung]]\n* [[National Science and Technology Museum]], [[Kaohsiung]]\n* [[National Museum of Marine Biology and Aquarium]], [[Pingtung County|Pingtung]]\n\n===Thailand===\n* [[Thailand National Science Museum|National Science Museum]], [[Pathum Thani Province|Pathum Thani]]\n\n==Middle East==\n\n===Egypt===\n\n* [[Planetarium Science Center]]\n\n===Israel===\n* [[Bloomfield Science Museum]], [[Jerusalem]]\n* [[Israel National Museum of Science, Technology, and Space]], [[Haifa]]\n\n==Africa==\n\n===South Africa===\n* [[MTN Sciencentre]], [[Cape Town]]\n* [https://www.sci-bono.co.za/ Sci-Bono Discovery Centre], [[Johannesburg]]\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of natural history museums]]\n* [[Planetarium]]\n* [[Science tourism]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://blogs.nature.com/u6e5b2ce1/2011/02/21/mapping-the-worlds-science-museums Map the World's Science Museums] on [http://blogs.nature.com/ Nature blogs]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Science Museums, List Of}}\n[[Category:Science museums| ]]\n[[Category:Lists of museums by subject]]\n[[Category:Science-related lists]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2011}}\nBelow is the '''list of science museums''' all over the world. See [[Science museum]] for definitions.